Following the reports of teenage boys slaughtering a girlfriend and burning her head for money ritual in Ogun State, Nigerian singer, Timaya, has urged Nigerians to be wary of the evil in the society as the crime rate is on rampage in the country. Reacting to the sad incident, Timaya via his Twitter wrote, “17 years old boys doing money ritual?? Innocent humans, killed for money, even your own homeboy can use you. “Watch out guys, it’s really cold outside.” Man United Confirm Mason Greenwood Wont Train Or Play Matches… Allow Peace To Reign In Bauchi, Mohammed Tells Opposition… Independent had reported on Saturday that there was pandemonium in Oke Aregba area of Abeokuta, the Ogun State capital, after teenage boys were caught burning the head of a girl, said to be in a relationship with one of them, for money ritual.